Join the Haas Fischer Center for Business Analytics for a Business x Data Science panel! 

Hear from six Haas faculty members about their research in business fields such as finance, marketing, and operations. Learn how they apply your technical skills in statistics and data science to research, their career journeys in academia, and more!

REGISTER HERE by NOV 9, 11:59pm PT: https://forms.gle/jda4MNFu5Zd5xW5A6. 

Facebook Event: https://facebook.com/events/s/business-x-ds-panel-with-haas-/2027040824120210/
